   [membertext.gif]

   An Invitation to Join the Herbert Hoover Presidential Library
                            Association

     Participate in the rich historical and cultural life of the Herbert
     Hoover Presidential Library-Museum and National Historic Site. Your
       membership opens a wonderful new world of special, members-only
                                 privileges

   Your Membership Supports . . .

     * Educational Programs
     * Special Exhibits
     * Conservation of Materials
     * Conferences and Workshops
     * Research Scholarships and Fellowships

    Learn more about the Association and view a list of coming events by
   visiting the Hoover Library Association's website, www.hooverassoc.org

